      <title>Polymarket 在预测投注审查期间屏蔽了法国用户</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-22/polymarket-blocks-french-users-amid-scrutiny-of-prediction-bets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在法国赌博监管机构日益严格的审查下，基于加密货币的预测市场 Polymarket 已阻止法国用户在该平台上进行新的投注。]]></description>
